
HOW TO ENABLE/DISABLE WINDOWS HIBERBOOT (AKA FASTBOOT)

  1. Open the Registry Editor (regedit.exe);

  2. Locate the hiberboot registry at
     HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Session Manager\Power 

  3. Open the HiberbootEnabled (DWORD) registry;

  4. Change the value to enable or disable windows hiberboot
     0 to disable;
     1 to enable.

